%description
ejabberd is a Free and Open Source distributed fault-tolerant
Jabber/XMPP server. It is mostly written in Erlang, and runs on many
platforms (tested on Linux, FreeBSD, NetBSD, Solaris, Mac OS X and
Windows NT/2000/XP).

